    "Readers can evaluate a short, well-targeted text span more quickly without decreasing the accuracy of judgement [10].",
    "Consequently, the fine-grained evidence is both efficient and effective for mitigating misinformation.To automate the management of online discussions, large language models (LLMs) can be employed to extract claims from user comments.",
